pl_output:
Usage: pass in any scriptors that you want to call, and/or, `Nmsg` with at least one of `Nto`, `Nchannel`.
If you passed in any scriptors, they will be called, with the same set of arguments as passed to this script.
Then, if you passed in `Nmsg`, a chats.send will be sent to `Nchannel` and/or a chats.tell will be sent to `Nto`.
